1. *Brod* je veoma velik. (The ship is very big.)
2. *Brodovi* su preplovili neke daleke more. (The ships have sailed across some distant seas.)
3. On je bio na *brodu* dve nedelje. (He was on the ship for two weeks.)
4. Oni su se iznenada pojavili na *brodu*. (They suddenly appeared on the ship.)
5. *Brodovima* su potrebne godine da stignu do svojih odredišta. (The ships take years to reach their destinations.)
6. Oni su se plašili da će *brodu* biti oštećen. (They were afraid that the ship would be damaged.)